================================================================================
KEY PATTERNS TO REMEMBER
================================================================================

1. Always use ChatRole enum: System, User, Assistant, Tool
2. ChatMessage contains multiple AIContent items (polymorphic)
3. ChatOptions can hold Tools and ToolMode for function calling
4. FunctionInvokingChatClient auto-invokes and resubmits
5. AIAgent is abstract - implement for custom logic
6. AgentSession is serializable via StateBag
7. Use ChatClientBuilder to create middleware pipelines
8. Structured output: use GetResponseAsync<T>
9. Streaming: check if ContentUpdate is TextContentUpdate
10. Always pass CancellationToken for async operations
